<div class="container">
    <header class="policy-header">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="lead mt-3">Committed to Protecting Your Privacy and Securing Your Data</p>
    </header>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us when using EShift, including your name, contact details, shipment information, and payment data. Additionally, we gather technical and usage data automatically to improve your experience.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name, address, email, phone number, payment info.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, and session duration.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and browser settings.</li>
            <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> With your permission, precise location data for live tracking and route optimization.</li>
            <li><strong>Transaction Records:</strong> Details about your shipment requests, loads, and payments.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>Your information helps us deliver, improve, and personalize our services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Operate and maintain our transport platform efficiently.</li>
            <li>Enhance user experience and tailor services to your needs.</li>
            <li>Process payments and send confirmations or invoices.</li>
            <li>Communicate updates, service alerts, and marketing with your consent.</li>
            <li>Analyze trends to improve system security and performance.</li>
            <li>Detect and prevent fraud or unauthorized activity.</li>
            <li>Meet legal obligations and enforce our policies.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h2>Who We Share Your Information With</h2>
        <p>We only share your data when necessary to provide our service or comply with the law:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>With transport providers for scheduling and delivery coordination.</li>
            <li>With you and authorized customers regarding job and shipment details.</li>
            <li>With trusted third-party vendors who support our platform (e.g., payment processors, hosting).</li>
            <li>During business transitions like mergers or acquisitions.</li>
            <li>When required by legal authorities or to protect rights and safety.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h2>Your Privacy Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your region, you may have rights to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access your personal information.</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your data.</li>
            <li>Restrict or object to processing of your data.</li>
            <li>Obtain a portable copy of your data.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise these rights, please contact our support team using the information below.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h2>How We Protect Your Data</h2>
        <p>We employ strong technical, administrative, and physical safeguards to protect your information. However, no method is completely secure, so please be cautious when sharing sensitive data online.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may revise this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here with the latest revision date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy or this policy, please reach out:</p>
        <p>
            <strong>EShift Support Team</strong><br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@EShift.com">privacy@EShift.com</a><br />
            Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567
        </p>
    </section>

    <p class="last-revised">Last Revised: July 17, 2025</p>
</div>
